  • Classes in tp.pr5 used by tp.pr5 
    Class and Description
    City
    This class represents the city where the robot is wandering.
    It contains information about the streets and the places in the city
    Direction
    An enum class that represents the compass directions (North, east, south and west) plus a value that represents an unknown direction.
    NavigationModule 
    Place
    It represents a place in the city.
    Places are connected by streets according to the 4 compass directions: North, East, South and West.
    PlaceInfo
    PlaceInfo defines a non-modifiable interface over a Place.
    PlaceType 
    RobotEngine
    This class represents the robot engine.

    StormType
